    <item>
      <title>大型银行希望减轻初级银行家的工作负担</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-12/big-banks-look-to-ease-junior-banker-workloads-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通和美国银行正在采取措施减轻初级银行家的工作量。摩根大通将在大多数情况下将初级银行家的工作时间限制为每周 80 小时。美国银行将改变其监控工作时间的方式。凯瑟琳·多尔蒂在“彭博未平仓合约”上发表了华尔街评论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-12/big-banks-look-to-ease-junior-banker-workloads-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 14:25:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国巴黎银行就供应过剩发出警告，美光科技罕见遭遇熊市预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/micron-gets-a-rare-bear-call-as-bnp-paribas-warns-on-oversupply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美光科技公司股价周四暴跌，这家计算机内存芯片制造商延续了近期的抛售趋势，因法国巴黎银行证券部警告称，该股表现将继续不及其他与人工智能相关的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/micron-gets-a-rare-bear-call-as-bnp-paribas-warns-on-oversupply</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 14:09:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济低迷致德国电力交易价格接近四个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/german-power-trades-at-four-month-low-amid-economic-gloom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于德国经济陷入困境有可能进一步抑制能源需求，德国未来一年的电力交易价格接近四个月来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/german-power-trades-at-four-month-low-amid-economic-gloom</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 12:04:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班耶 (Sibanye) 将削减产量以扭转美国钯矿的颓势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/sibanye-to-slash-output-in-bid-to-turn-around-us-palladium-mines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Sibanye Stillwater Ltd. 计划进一步重组其位于蒙大拿州的矿山，这可能会将钯和铂的产量减少 45%，以恢复盈利能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/sibanye-to-slash-output-in-bid-to-turn-around-us-palladium-mines</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 11:09:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Orcel 称德国政府知道裕信银行持有德国商业银行股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/germany-knew-unicredit-had-4-5-commerzbank-stake-orcel-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利联合信贷银行（UniCredit SpA）首席执行官安德烈亚·奥塞尔（Andrea Orcel）表示，联合信贷银行对德国商业银行的投资不应该让相关方感到意外，此举是为了打消一些担忧，此前该银行披露了其持有德国商业银行 9% 的股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/germany-knew-unicredit-had-4-5-commerzbank-stake-orcel-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 10:38:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
